quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  18,16,"Tuma nde wo…ó…óitino…óon …ďe e ko …ďe rewata kon ko woori Alla, …ďe soroyi ka fammeere Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende Makko nden O newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende"
  18,17,"Hi…óa yi'a naangi ngen si nge ∆īellitike hinge naayora ka fammeere ma…ď…ďe senngo √Īaamo, si hinge mutude nge mutiranay …ďe ka senngo nano, kam…ďe hi…ďe e yaajeende e …óun, …óun ko jeyaa…óun e Aayeeje Alla, on mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewu…óo, kala moO majjini a he…ďantaa mo hettu…óo fewnoowo. @Corrected"
  18,18,"Hi…óa sikka …ďe ko …ďe finu…ďe, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe …óaanii…ďe, Me…óen waylitira …ďe senngo √Īaamo e senngo nano, rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun no fonti kay…óe mun …óen ka dammbugal, si a ∆īellitike e ma…ď…ďe a huccitayno e ma…ď…ďe dogaa a heewayno kulol immorde e ma…ď…ďe"
  18,19,"Ko nii Men immintiniri …ďe fii yo …ďe lanndondir hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, wi'oowo wi'i immorde e ma…ď…ďe: \"No foti hewde ko √Īii…ďu…óon?\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Men √Īii…ďii √Īallal maa go…ó…óun e √Īallal.\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko √Īii…ďu…óon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon wonndude e …óii kaaki=ceede mon …óoo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri laa…ďude √Īaamitee, yo o addan on √Īaametee immorde e on …óon, yo o molto wata gooto so'u fii mon"
  18,20,"Pellet, kam…ďe si …ďe ∆īellitike e mon …ďe rajmay on, maa…óun …ďe rutta on e laawol ma…ď…ďe ngol, ontuma hara on maletaake poomaa"
